"title": "4657: horse",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4657: horse",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The animal most commonly associated with war and battle, the horse also appears figuratively in poetic and prophetic literature. Its domesticated usage was mainly for personal travel and the haulage of heavy loads.</p>\n<h2>The military use of horses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:1\">EXO 15:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:4\">JOS 11:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:14-2Kgs6:15\">2KI 6:14–6:15</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:9\">EXO 14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:28\">EXO 14:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:4\">DEU 11:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:16-Isa43:17\">ISA 43:16–43:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:1\">1KI 20:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:20-1Kgs20:21\">1KI 20:20–20:21</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:19-Job39:25\">JOB 39:19–39:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:6\">PSA 76:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:28\">ISA 5:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:13\">JER 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:9\">JER 46:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:21\">JER 51:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:4\">EZK 38:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:8\">HAB 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Disabling horses in wartime</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:6\">JOS 11:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:9\">JOS 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:4\">2SA 8:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:4\">1CH 18:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:10\">MIC 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings against reliance on horses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1\">ISA 31:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:16\">DEU 17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:7\">PSA 20:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:17\">PSA 33:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:10\">PSA 147:10</a></p>\n<h2>The ritual use of horses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:7-Esth6:9\">EST 6:7–6:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:11\">1SA 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:1\">2SA 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:4\">JER 22:4</a></p>\n<h2>Horses as a means of exchange and a measure of wealth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:17\">GEN 47:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:26\">1KI 4:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:19\">1KI 9:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:25-1Kgs10:26\">1KI 10:25–10:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:14\">2CH 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:28\">2CH 9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:7\">ISA 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Horses as a means of transport and for the haulage of loads</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:9\">2KI 5:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:20\">2KI 14:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:28\">2CH 25:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:10\">EST 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:14\">EST 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:7\">ISA 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:9\">ISA 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:20\">ISA 66:20</a></p>\n<h2>Harness and tackle for horses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:28\">2KI 19:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:13\">JOB 41:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:28\">ISA 30:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:29\">ISA 37:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:20\">REV 14:20</a></p>\n<h2>The figurative and prophetic use of horse imagery</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:2-Jas3:3\">JAS 3:2–3:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:14\">2KI 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:28\">ISA 28:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:4\">JOL 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:6-Zech1:8\">ZEC 1:6–1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:1-Rev6:8\">REV 6:1–6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:17\">REV 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:14\">REV 19:14</a></p>\n<h2>Heavenly horses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:11\">2KI 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:6\">2KI 7:6</a></p>",
